{"tid":1365323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]又勾結美國勢力 (好似好濫)","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:36:39.000Z","uid":184451,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45bd987d633f7af5b8f4d48f55f720e2d289fa7d","tid":1365323,"uid":184451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"搞咗咁多單美國白宮聯署，都十足港豬話齋未見有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔做無可能，做就仲有一線希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛有一個關於721元朗鄉黑合作恐怖襲擊的白宮聯署<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/prosecute-persons-organizations-involving-violence-attack-21jul-hk-are-terrorism-usc-2656f-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fprosecute-persons-organizations-involving-violence-attack-21jul-hk-are-terrorism-usc-2656f-1&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=6dfa1804\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/prosecute-persons-organizations-involving-violence-attack-21jul-hk-are-terrorism-usc-2656f-1</a><br />\n<br />\nOn July 21, a premeditated, politically motivated violence mob attack happened in Yuen Long, HK, made ten of civilians were injured. Through information available so far, high possible of evidence to claim that it is a conspiracy between HK Police Force, Pro-CCP legislators, triads, Shap Pat Heung Rural Committee (SPHRC) for instilling fear in supporters of Anti-extradition Bill Protest. This is a <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">State-Supported Terrorism incident and crime against humanity</span></span>.<br />\n<br />\nWe call for the US Government to follow 22 U.S.C. 2656f to <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">declare those persons and organizations involving in this attack as terrorism</span></span>, including but not limited to Legislator <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Junius Ho, Police Commanders LEE Hon-Man and YAU Nai-keung, and members of SPHRC</span></span>, and take appropriate actions to prosecute them for their crime commited.<br />\n<br />\n<ins>求其認真譯</ins><br />\n响7月21日，於香港元朗發生一個有預謀、有政治動機的暴徒發動暴力襲擊，導致數十位平民受傷。根據目前得到資訊，有相當可能認為是由香港警務處、親中共立法會議員、三合會黑幫、十八鄉鄉事委員會為恐嚇「反對逃犯條例修訂」的示威者聯合發動，是一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「政府支援的恐怖主義」及「反人類罪行」的行動</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我們促請美國政府根據美國法令22 U.S.C. 2656f  關於恐怖主義活動的定義，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將7月21日的在香港元朗發生的事件定性為恐怖襲擊</span></span>，並將包括但不限於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立法會議員何君堯，元朗警區指揮官李漢民、游乃強，十八鄉鄉事委員會</span></span> 等參與該次行動的人士及組織採聯適當的拘捕行動。<br />\n++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br />\n麻煩大家簽埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同SHARE 叫多啲人簽咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡快夠十萬數叫侵侵總統做嘢，又起碼俾大家多樣嘢响手<br />\n唔該唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05f3d406f6c5f0188a4732b05be1f3f97aaca14","tid":1365323,"uid":184451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec342d354391293005ae3cc119daff6c5cb122f","tid":1365323,"uid":184451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990d3bac2e27d148c19f8a6b723e5352584eddd2","tid":1365323,"uid":184451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd5b788a4dadab1c1ecd515b535c8d3acfcf08f","tid":1365323,"uid":267082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"SIGNED<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cQZgg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cQZgg6.jpg&h=bca612cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e28b4e61e2bdeeade1cc6c12dccceb8bb4c9b75","tid":1365323,"uid":184451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cd5b788a4dadab1c1ecd515b535c8d3acfcf08f","tid":1365323,"uid":267082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"SIGNED<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cQZgg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cQZgg6.jpg&h=bca612cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1fee8106059f81d6dc671cf3c9f9fd271230a8","tid":1365323,"uid":6840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"抗爭一定唔容易, 唔會一次成功, 所以要繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83200d75b7784c31693f1e7697c01583c92644d6","tid":1365323,"uid":184451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n唔該各位，唔好見<span style=\"color: red;\">P</span>就唔理我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2b794ad0348e07d047b2ef48a55e22f0181fb1","tid":1365323,"uid":184451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"PUSH"}]}